Try cleaning the project. I’m not sure what options your IDE has, but Eclipse has a clean option that will rebuild the project and recompile it (creating new class files).

Also: Some IDE’s execute their path a little differently than the normal environment. Try running it from just the .bat (Not saying compile, I’m saying run)
